# 🕹️ Circle Collector – A Pygame Strategy Game

Welcome to **Circle Collector**, a competitive and fast-paced Pygame-based arcade game where you race against a bot to collect and deliver circles. Customize speed, score goals, and enjoy immersive sound effects.

---

## 🎮 Game Features

- ✅ Collect colored circles before the bot does
- ✅ Drop them in your delivery zone to score
- ✅ Dynamic bot opponent with speed settings
- ✅ Missions with different speed & score rules
- ✅ Background music & action sound effects
- ✅ Works on Windows, macOS, Linux

---

## 🎯 How to Play

- 🟥 **Player 1 Controls:**
  - `Arrow Keys` → Move
  - `Z` → Pick circle
  - `Space` → Dash

- 🤖 **Bot Player** moves automatically and competes to collect circles.

- 🎯 Drop collected circles into your color zone to score points.
- 🏆 First to reach the set **win score** wins!

---

